[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0855","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0855.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1008","title":"xsoldier 0.96 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"xsoldier 0.96 版本程序在处理命令行参数时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 xsoldier 程序传递超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖返回地址从而劫持程序执行流，成功利用后可获取受影响系统（RedHat 6.2）的 root 权限。该漏洞利用条件为攻击者需拥有本地系统账户，无需其他特殊权限即可实施提权攻击。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1008"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-05-17T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:30.753","remediation":"升级 xsoldier 至 0.98 及以上版本，或移除 xsoldier 的 setuid 权限位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/xsoldier）以防止本地提权。如无需该游戏，直接通过 rpm -e xsoldier 卸载。建议升级操作系统至受支持的 Red Hat 或 RHEL 发行版。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=freebsd-security&m=94531826621620&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/871","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/229","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1008.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1008","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1008.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1008.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1008.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6ww3-wprw-46qp/GHSA-6ww3-wprw-46qp.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1008.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152300_152400.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0855.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0084","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0084.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0427","title":"Qualcomm Eudora 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Qualcomm Eudora 邮件客户端（包括 Eudora 4.1/4.2/4.3、Eudora Light 3.0、Eudora Pro 1.0）在处理附件时存在输入验证缺陷，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过发送带有超长文件名的恶意邮件附件触发该漏洞，导致邮件客户端崩溃或拒绝服务。由于对附件文件名字段长度缺乏有效校验，攻击者可构造特制邮件批量发送，使目标用户无法正常使用邮件客户端。该漏洞 CVSS v2 评分 7.5，危害等级高，且可能伴随部分机密性和完整性影响。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0427"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2000-05-01","updated":"2000-05-01","remediation":"升级至 Eudora 5.0 或更高版本（5.x/6.x 系列已修复此漏洞），并避免打开来源不明的包含超长附件名的邮件。由于 Eudora 已于 2006 年停止维护，建议迁移至 Thunderbird 等仍在安全更新的邮件客户端以防止后续安全风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0427.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0427","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0427.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0427.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qj8p-hjm8-996j/GHSA-qj8p-hjm8-996j.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0427.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--fc880cf5-abcd-4188-8098-16ea76f2ee08.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001327.txt","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0084.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0295","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0295.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0706","title":"Linux xmonisdn 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Linux xmonisdn 软件包存在环境变量处理缺陷，本地用户可通过修改 IFS（内部字段分隔符）或 PATH 环境变量来劫持程序执行流程，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞源于 xmonisdn 程序在执行系统命令时未正确清理环境变量，导致攻击者可通过设置恶意 PATH 或 IFS 变量使程序执行攻击者控制的恶意代码。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0706"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-27","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"xmonisdn 软件包已停止维护多年，建议立即移除该软件包。如系统仍需 ISDN 功能，可迁移至现代替代方案（如 modemmanager 或 networkmanager）。对于仍在使用该软件包的系统，应确保以非 root 用户运行，并严格限制系统命令执行时的环境变量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/583","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0706"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0295.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0280","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0280.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0701","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 无人值守安装敏感信息泄露漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 在进行无人值守安装后，系统会在本地保留包含敏感配置信息的安装文件（如 Unattended.txt 或 Sysprep.inf），其中可能明文存储本地管理员账户密码。攻击者若能够获取对该文件的读取权限，即可直接提取管理员密码，进而完全控制目标系统。该漏洞源于安装程序未对生成的配置文件设置足够访问限制，属于配置不当问题。CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高，影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统。建议删除安装后残留的配置文件或严格限制其访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0701"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2000-04-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:52.677","remediation":"完成 Windows NT 4.0 无人值守安装后，立即手动删除 %windir%\\system32\\$winnt$.inf 和 $nt4pre$.inf 文件，或使用文本编辑器打开删除其中包含的管理员密码等敏感信息。同时启用 Syskey 工具对 SAM 数据库进行二次加密保护，并限制普通用户对 system32 目录的读取权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ173039","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/626","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-036","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0701.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0701","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0701.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0701.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-26w9-58jr-4jc3/GHSA-26w9-58jr-4jc3.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0701.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--ce201f9a-05b7-4813-a26f-ecc530d4b35a.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001276.txt","https://github.com/chandanbn/notes/blob/90eb64532f7259c55e5531dfc2726d810d17ef6e/cve5-validation-errors-Jan27.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0280.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0280.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0264","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0264.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0695","title":"Sybase PowerDynamo 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Sybase PowerDynamo 个人 Web 服务器存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标发送包含多个 ../ 序列的特制 HTTP 请求，突破路径限制读取服务器上的任意文件（如配置文件、系统文件等），导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞利用方式简单，攻击门槛低，CVSS v2.0 评分 5.0。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0695"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2000-04-11","updated":"2000-04-11","remediation":"立即升级 Sybase PowerDynamo 至最新补丁版本（如 3.5.2 以上），该版本已修复 `../` 路径遍历问题。如产品已停止技术支持，应停止使用 PowerDynamo Personal Web Server，迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache 或 IIS），并在迁移前通过 Web 应用防火墙（WAF）配置规则拦截包含 `../` 的 URL 请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0695.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0695","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0695.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0695.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8fq5-wmgh-8gpf/GHSA-8fq5-wmgh-8gpf.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0695.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001275.txt","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/8358776d7db47304e3a87c0f78eff81411ac0e47/1999.tsv","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--e7de3a3f-5597-490f-927a-ffc41edce468.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0264.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0274","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0274.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0699","title":"Bluestone Sapphire Web 服务器会话劫持漏洞","description":"Bluestone Sapphire Web 服务器使用可轻易猜测的会话ID（Session ID）来标识用户会话，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过暴力猜测或预测会话ID的方式劫持其他用户的会话，从而获取未授权访问权限，可能导致敏感信息泄露或越权操作。该漏洞源于会话ID生成算法缺乏足够的随机性和熵。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0699"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-11","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"Bluestone Sapphire Web 服务器已停止维护且厂商已被收购，建议迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache Tomcat 或 Nginx），并在应用层实现安全的会话管理机制，包括使用强随机数生成器创建会话ID、启用 HTTPS 加密传输、设置会话超时和 HttpOnly 标志。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/623","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0699"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0274.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0785","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0785.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0979","title":"SCO Unixware 7.0/7.0.1/7.1/7.1.1 - Privileged Process调试导致权限提升漏洞","description":"该漏洞源于SCO Unixware系统中的特权进程机制，攻击者可通过调试器（如gdb）在特权进程执行前向_init插入陷阱，进而获得root权限。该漏洞影响范围涵盖SCO Unixware多个版本，攻击者需具备本地访问权限，通过调试器向_init插入恶意陷阱代码，绕过系统权限验证机制，最终获取系统管理员权限。漏洞利用可能导致系统完全被控制，攻击者可以任意修改系统文件、安装恶意程序或进行其他破坏性操作。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0979"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-11","updated":"2026-07-14","remediation":"升级到SCO Unixware最新支持版本，建议使用7.2及更高版本以获取安全修复。或者应用SCO官方发布的针对此漏洞的安全补丁包。确认系统中已应用所有最新安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T04:59:27.626521880+00:00","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/869","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94530783815434&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0785.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0525","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0525.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0790","title":"Netscape Navigator 浏览器 JavaScript 缓存信息泄露漏洞","description":"Netscape 浏览器存在信息泄露漏洞，远程攻击者可通过恶意网页中的 JavaScript 脚本访问用户浏览器缓存中的敏感信息，包括浏览历史记录、已访问页面内容等。该漏洞影响早期 Netscape 浏览器版本，攻击者只需诱使用户访问包含恶意脚本的网页即可利用，无需特殊权限。由于缓存可能包含私人数据，该漏洞会严重威胁用户隐私安全。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0790"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2000-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:03.810","remediation":"升级 Netscape Communicator 到 4.7 及以上版本，Netscape 已针对 JavaScript 读取缓存问题发布安全修复。如无法升级，可在浏览器设置中禁用 JavaScript 作为临时缓解措施。鉴于 Netscape 已停止维护，建议迁移到现代浏览器（如 Firefox、Chrome）以获得持续安全支持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://home.netscape.com/security/notes/jscachebrowsing.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ea7161c86d011c8f810b70db6eb52fc6fcb9878b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0790.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0790","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0790.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1e2d061a60b9c6823d20cc72e51f709fadad54d2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0790.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/ce70cbcf8165046f2229cbe0d9f53c47bf63ece0/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mvw7-68fw-g45r/GHSA-mvw7-68fw-g45r.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0790.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--55a0b034-c223-4289-b30c-2a9571d15929.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/8200d63179d89b9076027cd96356d55ef8a5349e/1999.tsv","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--55a0b034-c223-4289-b30c-2a9571d15929.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0525.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0262","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0262.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0693","title":"多款 Unix 系统 ToolTalk 共享库本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"ToolTalk 共享库在处理 TT_SESSION 环境变量时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向该环境变量传入超长字符串触发缓冲区溢出，从而实现权限提升并获得 root 权限。该漏洞影响 DIGITAL UNIX 4.0、AIX 4.3.2、CDE 2.1、IRIX 6.5.14、Solaris 7.0 及 SunOS 4.1.4 等多个 UNIX 系统，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限方可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0693"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-03-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.690","remediation":"Sun Solaris 7.0/SunOS 4.1.4 用户安装 Sun Security Bulletin #192 提供的补丁包；HP-UX/Digital UNIX 4.0 用户应用 HPSBUX9909-103 对应的补丁；AIX 4.3.2 用户安装 IBM APAR 补丁；IRIX 6.5.14 用户安装 SGI 安全补丁。临时缓解措施：以 root 执行 `chmod 555 /usr/dt/bin/ttsession && chmod -s /usr/dt/bin/ttsession` 移除 setuid 位，同时限制非信任用户本地登录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/192","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/641","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9909-103","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A4374","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19501","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ea7161c86d011c8f810b70db6eb52fc6fcb9878b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0693.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0693","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0693.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1e2d061a60b9c6823d20cc72e51f709fadad54d2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0693.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f2b1645d908a7e97140c0423b4430b70de9fefa0/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wjxh-cxm3-22mj/GHSA-wjxh-cxm3-22mj.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0693.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152200_152300.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0262.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0173","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0173.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0595","title":"Microsoft Windows NT/2000 页面文件信息泄露漏洞","description":"Windows NT 及 Windows 2000 操作系统在关机时未清除系统页面文件（pagefile.sys）中的残留数据，导致内存中的敏感信息（如明文密码、密钥、用户数据等）可能被写入磁盘并长期保留。本地攻击者在获取系统访问权限后可通过读取页面文件提取这些敏感信息，造成信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及 Windows 2000 系统，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0595"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2000-01-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.143","remediation":"通过本地安全策略启用「关机：清除虚拟内存页面文件」（路径：安全设置→本地策略→安全选项），或设置注册表 HKLM\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\Session Manager\\Memory Management\\ClearPageFileAtShutdown 为 1。建议升级至 Windows 2000 SP4 或更高版本以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/216","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0595.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0595","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0595.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0595.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0595.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-79qg-vhxm-8q4c/GHSA-79qg-vhxm-8q4c.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86259/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0173.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1609","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1609.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0992","title":"HP VirtualVault 未授权进程访问限制绕过漏洞","description":"HP VirtualVault 操作系统存在安全绕过漏洞。在安装了 PHSS_17692 补丁的环境中，未授权或低权限的本地进程可利用 Trusted Gateway Proxy (TGP) 组件绕过系统的访问控制限制，从而获取未授权的资源访问权限。该漏洞影响 HP VirtualVault 操作系统相关版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。厂商已发布补丁修复此问题。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0992"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-18T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:28.707","remediation":"立即安装 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9912-107 中指定的补丁（PHSS_18263 或更新版本），该补丁修复了 Trusted Gateway Proxy (TGP) 的访问控制绕过问题。在无法安装补丁的情况下，限制非授权用户对 TGP 服务的本地访问权限，审查并收紧 TGP 配置中的访问控制规则。由于 HP VirtualVault VVOS 已停止技术支持，建议迁移至受支持的安全操作系统平台。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9912-107","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0992.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0992","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0992.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0992.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0992.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0992.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87941/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--7e38d2e2-f104-4783-aa45-431b0eece3d7.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idbypass"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1609.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0839","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0839.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1002","title":"Netscape Navigator 邮件密码弱加密存储漏洞","description":"Netscape Navigator 浏览器在存储用户邮件密码时采用弱加密算法，导致本地攻击者能够通过分析加密数据恢复明文密码。该漏洞存在于密码存储机制中，攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限，利用弱加密算法的可逆特性即可获取用户凭证信息，可能导致邮箱账户被非法访问。受影响版本包括 Netscape Navigator 全版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1002"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.997","remediation":"立即停止使用 Netscape Navigator 内置邮件客户端收发邮件，迁移至 Mozilla Firefox、Google Chrome 等现代浏览器或 Thunderbird 等独立邮件客户端访问邮件服务。如暂无法迁移，在 Netscape 首选项中关闭密码记忆功能，每次手动输入邮箱密码，避免凭据持久化存储于本地弱加密文件中。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94536309217214&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94570673523998&w=2","http://www.rstcorp.com/news/bad-crypto.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1002.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1002","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1002.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1002.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1002.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wf2x-w2q8-7723/GHSA-wf2x-w2q8-7723.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1002.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152000_152100.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--d48d045b-59cc-4474-90a9-e6ede9ca2247.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0839.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0350","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0350.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0735","title":"KDE K-Mail 符号链接本地权限提升漏洞","description":"KDE K-Mail 在处理临时用户目录时存在符号链接（symlink）竞争条件漏洞，具有本地访问权限的攻击者可通过在临时目录中创建恶意符号链接，当 K-Mail 以更高权限写入临时文件时，攻击者可因此劫持文件写入操作，覆盖或创建任意系统文件，从而实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响 KDE 1.1/1.1.1、Caldera OpenLinux 1.3/2.2 及 RedHat Linux 6.0 等系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0735"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2000-01-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:56.883","remediation":"升级 KDE 至 2.0 及以上版本，K-Mail 在新版中已修复不安全的临时文件创建方式。如无法升级，可将 umask 设为 077 并使用 `export TMPDIR=/tmp/kmail-$USER` 为每个用户分配独立临时目录，降低 symlink 攻击风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/RHSA1999015_01.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/300","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19240","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0735.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0735","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0735.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0735.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6q2m-wvf7-77h8/GHSA-6q2m-wvf7-77h8.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0735.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_gainpre.txt","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0350.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0365","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0365.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0744","title":"Netscape Enterprise Server 及 FastTrack Server 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Netscape Enterprise Server 及 FastTrack Server 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的超长 HTTP GET 请求触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出，进而可能造成服务崩溃或以服务器进程权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Netscape Enterprise Server 3.6 SP2/4.0 及 FastTrack Server 2.0.1 等版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。攻击无需身份认证，仅需目标开放 HTTP 服务即可远程利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0744"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2000-01-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:57.993","remediation":"升级 Netscape Enterprise Server 至 4.1 及以上版本，或升级 FastTrack Server 至 2.0.2 及以上版本以修复缓冲区溢出。鉴于该产品已停止维护（原 Netscape/Sun/Oracle iPlanet 产品线已退役），建议迁移至受支持的现代 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server 或 Nginx）。临时缓解措施可在反向代理或 WAF 层面限制 HTTP GET 请求 URI 长度不超过 4096 字节。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/603","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19783","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0744.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0744","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0744.